(42, 'Civil Engg. Department', 'To impart quality teaching at the undergraduate and post-graduate levels to attain excellence and thus to empower students to meet the technological needs and socio-economic challenges', '<h1>CIVIL ENGINEERING DEPARTMENT</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A</strong><strong>ims and Objectives of the Department / Mission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Following are the long-range goals of the department</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" rowspan="2">\r\n			<p>To impart quality teaching at the undergraduate and post-graduate levels to attain excellence and thus to empower students to meet the technological needs and socio-economic challenges.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" rowspan="2">\r\n			<p>Expansion and diversification of programs at post-graduate level to suit technical advances with following specialisations.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Structural Engineering (in existence)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Soil Mechanics and Foundation Engineering (in existence)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Water Resources Engineering (in existence)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Environmental Engineering (Already proposed)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Transportation Engineering (To be started from 2006 &ndash; 07)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Surveying and Remote Sensing Engineering</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Earthquake Engineering</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Rock Mechanics</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n			<p>More extensive industrial liaison and strengthening of need-based research activities leading to&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n			<p>doctoral (in existence) and post-doctoral research in various infrastructural and other emerging areas of Civil Engineering.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n			<p>To evolve a system for the development of faculty members and other supporting staff in the department.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2">\r\n			<p>To promote and provide consultancy and testing facilities with a view to generate additional resources and to keep in touch with latest demands of the profession.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>INFRASTRUCTURAL DETAILS<br />\r\nSpace for Teaching and Learning</strong></p>\r\n\r\n