(65, 'R&D ECE Department', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>RESEARCH FACILITIES ECE</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The department provides research facilities in the following fields</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Reliability evaluation and optimization general system.</td>\r\n			<td rowspan="5">\r\n			<p><a href="http://nitkkr.ac.in/87etrxcommun.htm" target="_top"><img alt="&lt; Click Here &lt;&lt;" src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/communicationlab1.jpg" style="height:93px; width:125px" /></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Development of digital instruments and teaching aids.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Digital signal processing.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Redundancy techniques in digital circuits.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Fault detection in digital computers.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Characteristics of atmospheric noise and aids effect communications.</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>System Engineering .</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Antennas.</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td