(72, 'Humanities Department', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>DEPARTMENT OF HUMANITIES AND SOCIAL SCIENCES</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Aims &amp; Objectives of the department, Mission </strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>The Department integrates humanistic values and social concerns with technical education. It undertakes teaching and research programs in the area of English, Economics, Management and IPR.</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Undergraduate Courses</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the first six semesters, the following compulsory courses are taught to B. Tech. students of all branches :</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Communication Skills in English (one semester)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Engineering Economics (one semester)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Organizational Behaviour (one semester)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Business Management (one semester)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Electives</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the compulsory courses, the following electives are offered to students of the 7th and 8th semesters :</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Advanced Communication Skills in English</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Development and Planning in Indian Economy</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Entrepreneurship</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Modern Trends in Management</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Human Resource Management</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Industrial Social&nbsp; Responsibility</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Research Facilities</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The department offers facilities for Doctoral research in the following areas :</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Anglo Saxon and Medieval English (Pre-Chaucerian) Poetry, Applied Linguistics (English Language Teaching, Translation Studies)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Agricultural Economics, Industrial Economics, Indian Economy.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Human Resources Management and Industrial Relations.</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td><span style="font-family:arial; font-size:10pt">Finance Management, Marketing Management.</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>Intellectual Property Rights</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>R &amp; D work by Teachers</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>A.</td>\r\n			<td>1.</td>\r\n			<td>Completed: A Research Project on &lsquo;Impact of Intellectual Property Rights on Indian Agriculture-A Case Study of Haryana&rsquo; sponsored by MHRD, GOI.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>2.</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;A Research Project on &lsquo;Setting up of Depository on IPR Literature/Case Studies/Materials&rsquo; sponsored by MHRD (Copyright Division).</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>B.</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Paper published&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>:</strong> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;136</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>C.</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Conferences&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>:</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 154</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', '["74","73"]', 'department'),
