(84, 'Laboratory Computer Engineering Department', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>LABORATORY FACILITIES COMPUTER ENGINEERING DEPARTMENT</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>All the Labs of the department are well equipped with many modern facilities/utilities. The department has its own Local Area Network (Based on Ethernet) since 1995. This LAN currently supports Linux and Windows Server, all are inter-net-worked through switches &amp; around 450 nodes are connected to the above servers. (Labs and Faculty)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The department has its own intranet web server for internal services. The department has also received funds under TEQIP programme of MHRD. The laboratories being developed under this programme are</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Computer Networking Laboratory&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td rowspan="4">\r\n			<p><a href="http://nitkkr.ac.in/76comP.htm" target="_top"><img alt="&lt;&lt; Click Here &lt;&lt;" src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/comlab01.jpg" style="height:82px; width:125px" /></a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Application and System Software Laboratory&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Mobile Computing Laboratory</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Computer Hardware and Troubleshooting Laboratory</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Software&#39;s</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:1