(91, 'B.tech Electrical Engineering', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<p>The Department offers instructions at undergraduate and postgraduate levels with the aim of providing a sound background in the areas of Electrical Engineering. The Department offers B.Tech., M.Tech. and Ph.D. Programs in Electrical Engineering</p>\r\n\r\n<h1>B. TECH PROGRAMME</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Intake - 90</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Syllabi of the B. Tech is revised from time to time by our own faculty, however, suggestions of experts from Academic institutes and industry are taken, keeping in view the demand of the day. Courses designed are such&nbsp; that in general, hands on sessions in laboratory follow theory courses. Practical training is imparted to the students in industry during summers vacations. Students are assigned major projects which includes design, fabrication and Testing and development of software etc. Department offers departmental electives in final year leading to degree of electrical engineering with specialization in the following areas.</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Power Apparatus and Systems</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Electronics and Instrumentation</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Computer Applications</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/docRed.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Information and Control</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>Which helps them in good placement through campus. Apart form this students pursue for higher studies&nbsp; research both in India as well as <a name="abroad">abroad</a>.</p>\r\n', '["95","94","93","92","90","89"]', 'sidenav'),
