(97, 'Vibration Lab', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>VIBRATION LAB</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>This lab is provided with equipments to perform the experiments of Vibrations such as to determine the natural frequency of undamped free vibrations, damped vibrations, torsional vibrations of single rotor system and double pendulum system. Students also study the forced vibrations.<br />\r\nSome more equipments such as Three Rotor Torsional System, Coupled Pitching and Bouncing Motion Machine are being procured.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The lab is equipped with:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:51%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Slider Crank Mechanism</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Quick Return Mechanism</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Belt &amp; Pulley Mechanism</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Universal Coupling Apparatus</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Cam Follower Apparatus</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Reciprocating Mass Balancing Machine</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Rotating Mass Balancing Machine</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Whirling of Shaft</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nit