(110, 'ADVANCED WELDING LABORATORY ', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>ADVANCE WELDING LAB</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>In view of the emerging importance and the employment potential of&nbsp; the field of Welding Technology, efforts are being made to develop Advanced Welding Engineering Laboratory in the Department.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At present, the lab is equipped with the following welding equipment and testing facilies :-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Electric Arc Welding Equipment</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>M. I. G. Welding Equipment</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Welding Rectifiers</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Welding Transformers</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>S. A. W. Equipment</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Welding Manipulator</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Ultrasonic Testing Equipment</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Dye-Penetrant Test Equipment</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Magnetic Particle Testing Equipment</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbod