(102, 'THERMAL ENGINEERING LAB', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>THERMAL ENGINEERING LAB</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>The lab consists of IC Engine, Steam Power and Automobile Section. The IC Engine section has a large number of models, cut sections and experimental setups to make the students conversant with actual engines and measurement of their performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Steam Power section has a Nestler Boiler, Steam Turbine and Vertical Steam Engine. The lab has a number of boiler models and cut sections of various devices.</p>\r\n', 'null', 'sidenav'),
(103, 'REFRIGERATION & AIRCONDITIONING LAB', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>REFRIGERATION &amp; AIRCONDITIONING LAB</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>This lab is equipped to perform the experiments including the performance and study of basic components used in Refrigeration and Air Conditioning. The equipments include Refrigeration Test Rig, Water Cooler, Walk in Cooler, Simple Vapour Compression System, Domestic Refrigerator, Ice Plant, Cooling Tower, Vapour Absorption Refrigeration System, Blower Test Rig, Air Conditioner and Cut Sections of different components.</p>\r\n', 'null', 'sidenav'),
(104, 'HYDRAULIC MACHINE LAB', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>HYDRAULIC MACHINE LAB</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; It has a wide range of equipments such as</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Hydraulic Turbines</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Pelton, Francis and Kaplan Turbine</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Hydraulic Pumps</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Centrifugal Pumps, Reciprocating Pump and Gear Pump</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Other experimental equipments include Hydraulic Ram, Torque Converter, Deepwell Turbine Pump, Cavitation Test Rig and Wind Tunnel.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'null', 'sidenav'),
(105, 'HYDRAULIC MACHINE LAB', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>HYDRAULIC MACHINE LAB</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; It has a wide range of equipments such as</p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" style="width:100%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Hydraulic Turbines</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Pelton, Francis and Kaplan Turbine</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Hydraulic Pumps</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n			<td>Centrifugal Pumps, Reciprocating Pump and Gear Pump</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>Other experimental equipments include Hydraulic Ram, Torque Converter, Deepwell Turbine Pump, Cavitation Test Rig and Wind Tunnel.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 'null', 'sidenav'),
(106, 'COMPUTER AND AUTOMATION CENTER', 'National Institute of Technology.', '<h1>COMPUTER AND AUTOMATION CENTER</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Introduction</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Computer &amp; Automation is established to cater to the computational needs of B. Tech., M.Tech. &amp; research&nbsp; students of Mechanical Engineering Department. Students visit this centre for, honing their skills in C, mastering Computer Aided Design software, computing numerical solutions and&nbsp; for their dissertation &amp; project works.&nbsp;&nbsp; All systems are placed on LAN and are provided with Internet connectivity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Amenities:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" style="width:47%">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Pentium IV</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>07</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Pentium III</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>07</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>IBM Server</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>01</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Laser Printer</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>01</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Dot Matrix Printers</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>02</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Inkjet printer</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>01</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img src="http://nitkkr.ac.in/images/dotGrey.gif" style="height:10px; width:16px" /></td>\r\n			<td>Scan